    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/ab0c4d43367d18253c032bec45ddce9d.poster.avif?t=1663183651\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/ab0c4d43367d18253c032bec45ddce9d.webm?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/ab0c4d43367d18253c032bec45ddce9d.mp4?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Genre and inspiration</h2>Horror of Minos is a Penumbra and Amnesia inspired story driven, single player, first person horror game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Contributing artists</h2>Special thanks to the following contributors<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Javi Rodriguez (aka McGybeer)</strong> for the 3D model for the guardians.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ancient puzzles</h2>You will need to solve ancient puzzles in order to make your way thorough the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/194ba773933ae7846138c0984d6a283c.poster.avif?t=1663183651\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/194ba773933ae7846138c0984d6a283c.webm?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/194ba773933ae7846138c0984d6a283c.mp4?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sanity System</h2>As you explore the game, any unsettling events, danger or proximity to disturbing objects will lower your sanity. This will cause visual and audible sideffects that can impair your ability to find your way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/e05cc8b0265a8310bba920a3e978a4dc.poster.avif?t=1663183651\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/e05cc8b0265a8310bba920a3e978a4dc.webm?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/e05cc8b0265a8310bba920a3e978a4dc.mp4?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Generation</h2>In order to make your experience more frightning and unique, some parts of the game generate procedurally. Depending on the initial seed, the mazes and events will be slightly different when you play. Moreover, the level will change multiple times as you play, misguiding your sense of direction and removing the abilty to retrace your steps.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/f0d93f4146914fed90208c091cb4a964.poster.avif?t=1663183651\" width=600 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/f0d93f4146914fed90208c091cb4a964.webm?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792210/extras/f0d93f4146914fed90208c091cb4a964.mp4?t=1663183651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>You are the only survivor from a team of explorers set to discover the misteries of a secret island.<br>It is rumored this is the island where the real Labyrinth of Minotaur was built by King Minos of Ancient Greece.<br>You must find out what happened to your team and what lurks beneath this forgotten island.",
